creator: Dunzo Digital
descriptionHtml:

- Get food delivery from top restaurants in the city

Why Dunzo? Glad you asked!

- We're the fastest; get home delivery in 45 minutes
- No order is too small for us; we'll deliver anything

- Save big; get up to 50% OFF on food, groceries and more
- Make payments online for a hassle-free experience and enjoy cashback from Paytm, Amazon Pay, Simpl, Lazy Pay and more

Order Food Online

Order food online from restaurants near and around you. Get home delivery in 45 minutes. Unlike other food delivery apps, you can order from ANY restaurant. Enjoy online food delivery from neighbourhood local joints, cafes, fine-dining restaurants, and fast-food chains like Dominos, KFC, Burger King, Pizza Hut, FreshMenu, Mc Donald’s, Subway, Faasos, Taco Bell and more.

This is the online food delivery app for every mood. Hot coffee? Spicy biryani? Cheesy pizzas & juicy burgers? Or some healthy salads & juices? You’ll find all your favourite food & beverages on Dunzo. With this food home delivery app, get any cuisines delivered to your doorstep including North Indian, Chinese, South Indian, and even foreign cuisines such as Thai, Vietnamese, and American. Whether it's breakfast, lunch, dinner, an evening snack, or late-night cravings, this online food delivery app will come to your rescue.

Order Grocery Online

Now buy groceries online on Dunzo - shop for grocery, fruits & vegetables, beauty & wellness, personal care, home & household essentials, diapers & baby care, pet care, organic products, meats and seafood on this grocery app. Enjoy grocery delivery to your home in 45 minutes. We’ll deliver even a single item both from your favourite local grocery stores near and around you and top supermarkets in the city.

Buy groceries online through this grocery app including products from Patanjali, Aashirvaad, Saffola, Fortune, Nestle, Amul, Mother Dairy, Coke, Pepsi, Bisleri, Colgate, Dabur, Surf Excel, Maggi, Vim, Haldiram's, Kellogg’s, Nescafe and Pampers amongst other leading brands. Dunzo is the only grocery shopping app you’ll ever need. Think of us as your online grocery store and supermarket.

Order Medicines Online

Dunzo is an online chemist in your pocket; you’ll never have to run from one chemist to the next again. Order Allopathic medicines, Homeopathic pills, Ayurvedic herbs, and Over-The-Counter (OTC) health products online from trusted chemists like Apollo Pharmacy, Wellness Forever and Myra Medicines. Get home delivery in 45 minutes.

Avail better discounts and savings on medical bills compared to the local pharmacy. Save up to 50% on medicines and get the lowest prices on OTC health products from brands like Dabur, Himalaya, Piramal, Pediasure, Sri Sri Tattva, Organic India, HealthVit, Baidyanath, Patanjali, and others.

Send Packages Within Your City

Dunzo allows you to send packages anywhere across the city. Use us to pick up and drop off laundry, get forgotten keys, send lunch boxes from home to office, send or collect items for repair or even deliver documents or parcels to clients.

Book a Bike Taxi

Zip through traffic and get to anywhere in the city using Dunzo Bike Taxi. It’s the fastest and cheapest way to commute in the city. Don’t waste time waiting for a cab; hop on a Dunzo Bike Taxi now! Available in Gurgaon, Noida & Hyderabad only.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
An OTP is a great pick-up line

With this update, we have introduced an option to assign an OTP to your order when you are sending packages via Dunzo. Users will be able to opt for a verification code that ensures your order is safely received at the other end- truly a courteous way to pick up your delivery.

Other upgrades include improvements to the payment feature and home page that enhances your experience on our platform, among other backend changes and bug fixes.

Dunzo is a 24x7 delivery app that delivers anything to your doorstep in 30 minutes. Grocery shopping or food delivery, Dunzo is the only delivery app you'll ever need.

- Go online grocery shopping at local stores near you
- Get food delivery from top restaurants in the city
- Get medicines delivery from local chemists near you
- Send packages anywhere within the city
- Book a bike ride to go anywhere within the city 

Why Dunzo?

- We're the fastest; get home delivery in 30 mins
- No order is too small; we'll deliver anything
- Order from anywhere in the city; we'll deliver
- Save big; get up to 50% OFF on food, grocery shopping & more
- Make payments online for a smooth experience & enjoy cashback from Paytm, Amazon Pay, Simpl, LazyPay & more

Order Grocery Online

Buy groceries online on this simple grocery delivery app - shop for groceries, fruits & vegetables, beauty & wellness, personal care, home & household essentials, diapers, baby care, pet care, organic products, meats & seafood on this online grocery app. Enjoy grocery delivery to your home in 30 mins by ordering on the most convenient grocery delivery app in town! Enjoy grocery delivery of even a single item with your online grocery app. With this grocery delivery app, get groceries, fruits & vegetables delivered from your local grocery stores, fruits & vegetables shop, and top supermarkets.

Simplify buying groceries through this online grocery app. Enjoy grocery delivery of products from Patanjali, Aashirvaad, Saffola, Fortune, Nestle, Amul, Mother Dairy, Coke, Pepsi, Bisleri, Colgate, Dabur, Surf Excel, Maggi, Vim, Haldiram's, Kellogg’s, Nescafe, Pampers & other leading brands through this grocery delivery app. Use this grocery shopping app to buy items from shops near & around you. With this online grocery app, shop for items from your supermarkets, fruits & vegetables shops with instant fruits & vegetables and grocery delivery. This grocery shopping app lets you order groceries any time!

Order Food Online

Order food online from restaurants near you. Get home delivery in 30 mins. Unlike most food delivery apps, you can order from ANY restaurant. Enjoy online food delivery from neighbourhood local joints, cafes, fine-dining restaurants, & fast-food chains like Dominos, KFC, Burger King, Pizza Hut, FreshMenu, Mc Donald’s, Subway, Faasos, Taco Bell & more.

This is the online food delivery app for every mood. Hot coffee? Spicy biryani? Cheesy pizzas & juicy burgers? Or some healthy salads & juices? You’ll find your favourite food & beverages on Dunzo. With this food home delivery app, get any cuisine delivered to your doorstep including North Indian, Chinese, South Indian, & even foreign cuisines such as Thai, Vietnamese, & American. Whether it's breakfast, lunch, dinner, an evening snack, or late-night cravings.

Order Medicines Online

Dunzo is an online chemist in your pocket; you’ll never have to run from one chemist to the next again. Order Allopathic medicines, Homeopathic pills, Ayurvedic herbs, & Over-The-Counter (OTC) health products online from trusted chemists like Apollo Pharmacy, Wellness Forever & Myra Medicines. Get home delivery in 30 mins.

Save up to 50% on medicines & get the lowest prices on OTC health products from brands like Dabur, Himalaya, Piramal, Pediasure, Sri Sri Tattva, Organic India, HealthVit, Baidyanath, Patanjali, & others.

Send Packages Within Your City

Dunzo allows you to send packages anywhere across the city. Use us to pick up & drop off laundry, get forgotten keys, send lunch boxes from home to office, send or collect items for repair or deliver documents or parcels to clients.

Book a Bike Taxi

Zip through traffic & get to anywhere in the city with Dunzo Bike Taxi. The fastest & cheapest way to commute in the city. Don’t waste time waiting for a cab; hop on a Dunzo Bike Taxi.

--

Available in Bangalore, Mumbai, Gurgaon, Delhi, Hyderabad, Pune, Chennai, & Jaipur.

Stay close to the router when updating

Nope, this update is not heavy.
In fact, it only contains things that you absolutely need- improvements that help you save money and the usual bug fixes without which our lives would be darn boring.

Do you know what else we absolutely need? A router with a short-range, so you don’t even think about leaving the house.

Don't take chances, stay in. Stay safe.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:

Yes, we can bring you silverware, but not the one you’re expecting.

How to cook a bug-free update
Take a fresh set of problem statements and dice them nicely.
Pour lines of code that improve stability and speed, and let it simmer for a bit.
Now add the home page update that improves the app reload into the mix and stir it gently.
Cook until it’s golden brown and sprinkle security updates for taste.
Garnish the update with flakes of quintessential bug fixes.
Serve it hot & fresh on Play Store.

Take a fresh set of problem statements and dice them nicely.

Serve it hot & fresh on Play Store.

Harri Partner & Chamber of Updates
Things get a little out of hand when Ronak’s younger sister orders a copy of Champak but forgets to carry enough Galleons to pay. Harri realises that he can help her with swift payments using the Quick Pay feature. Elsewhere, Harmeen learns new charms to help her remember addresses & discover new offers. The three set out on an adventure to thwart the plans of the mysterious bugs within the chamber beneath.

Things get a little out of hand when Ronak’s younger sister orders a copy of Champak but forgets to carry enough Galleons to pay. Harri realises that he can help her with swift payments using the Quick Pay feature. Elsewhere, Harmeen learns new charms to help her remember addresses & discover new offers. The three set out on an adventure to thwart the plans of the mysterious bugs within the chamber beneath.

title: Dunzo: Grocery Shopping & More

creator: Dunzo Digital
descriptionHtml:
Dunzo is a 24x7 delivery app that delivers anything to your doorstep instantly. From shopping for Grocery to Fruits & Vegetables, Meat & more, Dunzo is the only delivery app you'll ever need.

- Shop for Grocery, Fruits & Vegetables from local stores
- Order Meat & Fish from the best stores in town
- Get medicines delivered from local chemists near you
- Send packages anywhere within the city
- Get food delivery from top restaurants in the city

⚡Why Dunzo?

- We're the fastest; get home delivery instantly
- No order is too small; we'll deliver anything
- Order from anywhere in the city; we'll deliver
- Save big; get up to 50% OFF on Groceries, Fruits, Veggies & more
- Make payments online for a smooth experience & enjoy cashback from Google Pay, Paytm, Amazon Pay, CRED Pay, Simpl, LazyPay & more

⚡Dunzo Daily
Dunzo Daily is your all-in-one online supermarket with 19 min doorstep delivery. Enjoy instant delivery of the freshest grocery delivered to your doorstep. Order everything from Fruits, Vegetables, Meat, Pet Supplies & other daily needs. We ensure that you get the freshest produce of daily essentials, delivered right to your doorstep. With great offers & products ranging from breakfast items, fresh fruits and vegetables to household supplies, you can get all your shopping done & still make a saving. Dunzo Daily is currently available only in Bangalore.


🛒Order Grocery Online

Grocery shopping will never be the same once you start using this online delivery app. Enjoy the convenience of online grocery shopping and have it delivered to your doorstep instantly. From daily essentials to stocking up the kitchen, order groceries online and get the freshest produce in town.

Order grocery online and get products from Aashirvaad, Saffola, Fortune, Nestle, Amul, Mother Dairy, Coke, Pepsi, Bisleri, Colgate, Patanjali, Dabur, Surf Excel, Maggi, Vim, Haldiram's, Kellogg’s, Nescafe, Pampers & other leading brands.

Get grocery shopping done & get it delivered in just 19 min in Bangalore & within 35 min in Hyderabad, Delhi, Gurgaon, Pune, Mumbai & Chennai.

🥦🥕Order Fruits & Vegetables Online

Order the freshest Fruits & Vegetables from local stores near you using this online delivery app. Now shopping for Fruits & Vegetables is so easy; just place an order on the app, & get it home delivered instantly.

🥛Order Milk & Dairy Online

Order Milk & Dairy products online with ease, and get it all delivered home instantly. Now you will never run out of Dairy products at home when you can just place an order on Dunzo. Enjoy milk delivery from brands like Nandini, Milky Mist, Amul & more.

🍗Order Meat, Chicken & Fish Online

Get the freshest Meat, Chicken & Fish delivered to your doorstep instantly. Enjoy online delivery of meat like never before with this instant delivery app. If you enjoy fresh fish, you will definitely enjoy this online fish delivery we offer. Now order Chicken online or Meat; it will reach your doorstep in no time.

🍔Order Food Online

Order food online from any restaurant & get home delivery instantly. Enjoy online food delivery from neighbourhood local joints, cafes, fine-dining restaurants, & fast-food chains like Dominos, KFC, Burger King, Pizza Hut, FreshMenu, Mc Donald’s, Subway, Faasos, Taco Bell & more.

💊Order Medicines Online

Dunzo is an online chemist in your pocket. Order Allopathic medicines, Homeopathic pills, Ayurvedic herbs, & Over-The-Counter (OTC) health products online from trusted chemists like Apollo Pharmacy, Wellness Forever & Myra Medicines. Get home delivery instantly.

📦Send Packages Within Your City

Dunzo allows you to send packages anywhere across the city. Use us to pick up & drop off laundry, get forgotten keys, send lunch boxes from home to office, send or collect items for repair or deliver documents or parcels to clients.

--

Dunzo is available in Bangalore, Mumbai, Gurgaon, Delhi, Hyderabad, Pune & Chennai

If you consider yourself a frood, and would like to excuse yourself from an uncouth situation, be aware that such a task can only be carried out by an intelligent dolphin or a diligent friend. On the off-chance that you want to delete your Dunzo account, the task is much simpler: You can provide your reason for exit, find the closest ‘delete button’, and excuse yourself. Do not leave your towel behind.

title: Dunzo: Grocery Shopping & More

creator: Dunzo Digital
descriptionHtml:
Dunzo is a 24x7 delivery app that delivers anything to your doorstep instantly. From shopping for Grocery to Fruits & Vegetables, Meat & more, Dunzo is the only delivery app you'll ever need.

- Shop for Grocery, Fruits & Vegetables from local stores
- Order Meat & Fish from the best stores in town
- Get medicines delivered from local chemists near you
- Send packages anywhere within the city
- Get food delivery from top restaurants in the city

⚡Why Dunzo?

- We're the fastest; get home delivery instantly
- No order is too small; we'll deliver anything
- Order from anywhere in the city; we'll deliver
- Save big; get up to 50% OFF on Groceries, Fruits, Veggies & more
- Make payments online for a smooth experience & enjoy cashback from Google Pay, Paytm, Amazon Pay, CRED Pay, Simpl, LazyPay & more

⚡Dunzo Daily
Dunzo Daily is your all-in-one online supermarket with 19 min doorstep delivery. Enjoy instant delivery of the freshest grocery delivered to your doorstep. Order everything from Fruits, Vegetables, Meat, Pet Supplies & other daily needs. We ensure that you get the freshest produce of daily essentials, delivered right to your doorstep. With great offers & products ranging from breakfast items, fresh fruits and vegetables to household supplies, you can get all your shopping done & still make a saving. Dunzo Daily is currently available only in Bangalore.


🛒Order Grocery Online

Grocery shopping will never be the same once you start using this online delivery app. Enjoy the convenience of online grocery shopping and have it delivered to your doorstep instantly. From daily essentials to stocking up the kitchen, order groceries online and get the freshest produce in town.

Order grocery online and get products from Aashirvaad, Saffola, Fortune, Nestle, Amul, Mother Dairy, Coke, Pepsi, Bisleri, Colgate, Patanjali, Dabur, Surf Excel, Maggi, Vim, Haldiram's, Kellogg’s, Nescafe, Pampers & other leading brands.

Get grocery shopping done & get it delivered in just 19 min in Bangalore & within 35 min in Hyderabad, Delhi, Gurgaon, Pune, Mumbai & Chennai.

🥦🥕Order Fruits & Vegetables Online

Order the freshest Fruits & Vegetables from local stores near you using this online delivery app. Now shopping for Fruits & Vegetables is so easy; just place an order on the app, & get it home delivered instantly.

🥛Order Milk & Dairy Online

Order Milk & Dairy products online with ease, and get it all delivered home instantly. Now you will never run out of Dairy products at home when you can just place an order on Dunzo. Enjoy milk delivery from brands like Nandini, Milky Mist, Amul & more.

🍗Order Meat, Chicken & Fish Online

Get the freshest Meat, Chicken & Fish delivered to your doorstep instantly. Enjoy online delivery of meat like never before with this instant delivery app. If you enjoy fresh fish, you will definitely enjoy this online fish delivery we offer. Now order Chicken online or Meat; it will reach your doorstep in no time.

🍔Order Food Online

Order food online from any restaurant & get home delivery instantly. Enjoy online food delivery from neighbourhood local joints, cafes, fine-dining restaurants, & fast-food chains like Dominos, KFC, Burger King, Pizza Hut, FreshMenu, Mc Donald’s, Subway, Faasos, Taco Bell & more.

💊Order Medicines Online

Dunzo is an online chemist in your pocket. Order Allopathic medicines, Homeopathic pills, Ayurvedic herbs, & Over-The-Counter (OTC) health products online from trusted chemists like Apollo Pharmacy, Wellness Forever & Myra Medicines. Get home delivery instantly.

📦Send Packages Within Your City

Dunzo allows you to send packages anywhere across the city. Use us to pick up & drop off laundry, get forgotten keys, send lunch boxes from home to office, send or collect items for repair or deliver documents or parcels to clients.

--

Dunzo is available in Bangalore, Mumbai, Gurgaon, Delhi, Hyderabad, Pune & Chennai

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Not the Last of Our Update
While Joel & Ellie’s journey may have come to an end (for now), our journey to give you a seamless experience on the app never ends; and this is why you have another fungi-free and bug-free update. We have also made improved the Hyperverge SDK and refactored the payment section to enable smoother transactions on the platform. Ellie may not remember what happened at Salt Lake City, but with this update, we have plugged all the memory leaks using smart codes.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Update as yummy as Vada Pav
Make a ball-sized mixture of the finest codes that improve features like Quick Category Access and Interrupt Crash Fix, dip it in batter and let it rest. Now drop them in hot & piping features, and stir them gently until you fry them to perfection. Slit the pav and apply a fine layer of Sponsored SKU chutney and slide the vada with the codes. Add a single file of fried PIs to add a bit of spice and now you have a snack that even Tim Cook can’t deny.
